\c 1
\s USolomoni ucela ukuthi anikwe ingqondo yokuqedisisa
\p
\v 1 USolomoni indodana kaDavida waseqina embusweni wakhe\x + 1 Kho. 2.46.\x*, leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe yayilaye\x + Gen. 39.2.\x*, yamenza waba mkhulu kakhulu\x + 1 Lan. 29.25.\x*.
\v 2 USolomoni wasekhuluma kuIsrayeli wonke, kubaphathi bezinkulungwane labamakhulu, lakubahluleli, lakuzo zonke induna kuIsrayeli wonke, inhloko zaboyise\x + 1 Lan. 27.1.\x*.
\v 3 USolomoni lebandla lonke laye basebesiya endaweni ephakemeyo eyayiseGibeyoni\x + 1.13. 1 Kho. 3.4.\x*; ngoba kwakukhona lapho ithente lenhlangano kaNkulunkulu uMozisi inceku yeN\nd kosi\nd* alenzayo enkangala\x + 1 Lan. 21.29.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa uDavida wayewenyusile umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 6.2,17. 1 Kho. 3.15. 1 Lan. 15.1.\x* uvela eKiriyathi-Jeyarimi\x + Josh. 9.17.\x*, wawusa lapho uDavida ayewulungisele khona, ngoba wayewumisele ithente eJerusalema.
\v 5 Lelathi lethusi\x + Eks. 27.1,2. 38.1,2.\x*, uBhezaleli indodana kaUri indodana kaHuri ayelenzile, walibeka phambi kwethabhanekele leN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 31.2.\x*\nd*; uSolomoni lebandla badinga-ke kulo\x + 1 Lan. 13.3.\x*.
\v 6 USolomoni wasesenyukela lapho elathini lethusi phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* elalisethenteni lenhlangano, wanikela phezu kwalo iminikelo yokutshiswa eyinkulungwane\x + 1 Kho. 3.4.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Ngalobobusuku uNkulunkulu wabonakala kuSolomoni, wathi kuye: Cela engingakupha khona\x + 1 Kho. 3.5-14.\x*.
\v 8 USolomoni wasesithi kuNkulunkulu: Wena wenzele uDavida ubaba umusa omkhulu, wangenza ngaba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 9 Khathesi, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu, kaliqiniswe ilizwi lakho kuDavida ubaba\x + 6.17. 1 Kho. 8.26.\x*, ngoba wena ungenze ngaba yinkosi phezu kwabantu abanengi ngangothuli lomhlabathi.
\v 10 Khathesi ngipha inhlakanipho lolwazi ukuze ngiphume ngingene phambi kwalababantu; ngoba ngubani ongehlulela lababantu bakho abakhulu \add kangaka\add*?
\v 11 UNkulunkulu wasesithi kuSolomoni: Ngenxa yokuthi lokhu bekusenhliziyweni yakho, njalo ungacelanga inotho, ingcebo, lodumo, lempilo yezitha zakho, futhi ungacelanga insuku ezinengi, kodwa uzicelele inhlakanipho lolwazi ukuze wahlulele abantu bami engikwenze waba yinkosi phezu kwabo\x + 1.12. Josh. 22.8. Ezra 6.8. 7.26. Tshu. 5.19. 6.2.\x*:
\v 12 Inhlakanipho lolwazi ukuphiwe; ngizakunika futhi inotho lengcebo lodumo\x + 1.12. Josh. 22.8. Ezra 6.8. 7.26. Tshu. 5.19. 6.2.\x*, angazange abe lakho okunjalo amakhosi ayengaphambi kwakho, langemva kwakho kakuyikuba khona okunjalo\x + 9.22. 1 Lan. 29.25.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Wasebuya uSolomoni evela endaweni ephakemeyo eseGibeyoni waya eJerusalema, evela phambi kwethente lenhlangano; wasebusa phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 14 USolomoni wasebuthanisa izinqola labagadi bamabhiza\x + 9.25-28. 1 Kho. 10.26-29.\x*; wayelezinqola ezingamakhulu alitshumi lane, labagadi bamabhiza abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi lambili\x + 9.25. 1 Kho. 4.26. 1 Kho. 10.26.\x*; wasekubeka emizini yezinqola, njalo kanye lenkosi eJerusalema\x + 1 Kho. 9.19.\x*.
\v 15 Inkosi yasisenza isiliva legolide eJerusalema kwaba njengamatshe, njalo wenza imisedari yaba njengemikhiwa yesikhamore esesihotsheni, ngobunengi.
\v 16 Wasengenisa ngokuthenga amabhiza avela eGibhithe, ayengekaSolomoni, lelembu elicolekileyo; labathengi benkosi babelithatha ilembu elicolekileyo ngentengo.
\v 17 Basebesenyusa bekhupha inqola eGibhithe nga\add \w mashekeli\w**\add* esiliva angamakhulu ayisithupha, lebhiza nga\add mashekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amahlanu. Ngokunjalo ba\add ku\add*khuphela wonke amakhosi amaHethi lamakhosi eSiriya ngesandla sabo.
